item.title: Algorithms and data structures
item.description: I came across a youtube channel by Mr. Abdul Bari. It is highly recommended for anyone who want to learn or do a refresher on algorithms and datastructure. Mr. Bari is an excellent teacher and his teaching style is unique and he effortlessly takes you through complex concepts. Do watch his channel.
